WEBVTT

01:43.080 --> 01:45.000
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL
HIDDEN LOVE BY ZHU YI

01:54.440 --> 01:55.920
It should make you feel better.

01:59.360 --> 02:00.680
The doctor said to take two pills.

02:18.480 --> 02:20.240
Well? Do you feel better?

02:21.800 --> 02:23.080
It doesn't work immediately.

02:26.440 --> 02:28.680
Jiaxu, you don't need to worry about me.

02:30.080 --> 02:32.040
I think that milk tea is pretty tasty.

02:32.120 --> 02:33.680
Do you still want to have milk tea?

02:33.760 --> 02:35.240
No. It was my first time trying it.

02:35.320 --> 02:36.560
I was just

02:36.640 --> 02:38.720
giving you my opinion.

02:40.360 --> 02:41.600
I won't have it again.

02:41.680 --> 02:43.160
The last time I had milk,

02:43.240 --> 02:44.160
I threw up all night.

02:47.720 --> 02:49.800
Didn't I buy milk for you before?

02:59.840 --> 03:00.840
Did you drink it?

03:00.920 --> 03:01.840
No.

03:07.720 --> 03:09.200
My classmate drank it.

03:10.400 --> 03:11.960
She threw away the bottle too.

03:12.720 --> 03:15.040
It was pointless to keep it anyway.

03:18.600 --> 03:20.280
You should've told me

03:20.360 --> 03:21.960
that you can't have milk.

03:22.040 --> 03:23.480
I didn't drink it anyway.

03:24.160 --> 03:25.560
I'll take note of it next time.

03:26.120 --> 03:28.040
I was careless today.

03:28.600 --> 03:30.160
Remember to check

03:30.240 --> 03:31.800
before you drink something next time

03:31.880 --> 03:33.240
or it will be problematic for you.

03:39.680 --> 03:40.920
I'll take you back to your dorm.

03:43.120 --> 03:43.960
Let's go.

03:53.240 --> 03:55.080
Stop scratching.

03:55.160 --> 03:56.600
It will only get worse.

03:56.680 --> 03:57.840
You will get rashes again.

03:57.920 --> 04:00.400
I'm not scratching. I just feel hot.

04:09.200 --> 04:10.080
Be a good girl.

04:14.400 --> 04:15.280
Let's go.

04:28.520 --> 04:29.360
What's so funny?

04:31.240 --> 04:33.080
It's like you're walking your dog.

04:36.280 --> 04:37.120
Yes.

04:37.800 --> 04:39.240
I'm walking a little dog

04:40.160 --> 04:41.520
who eats indiscriminately.

04:52.160 --> 04:53.160
Jiaxu.

04:58.320 --> 05:01.440
Why did you tell your colleagues today

05:01.520 --> 05:02.680
that I am your friend?

05:03.600 --> 05:04.520
In the past,

05:07.240 --> 05:08.840
didn't you always tell other people

05:09.800 --> 05:10.920
that I am your sister?

05:16.520 --> 05:18.080
Do you really take me for your brother?

05:31.040 --> 05:31.960
Sang Zhi.

05:48.920 --> 05:49.840
It's nothing.

05:50.440 --> 05:51.280
Let's go.

06:03.000 --> 06:04.680
Your birthday is coming up, right?

06:05.360 --> 06:07.880
I guess I can't get you
a birthday cake then.

06:08.640 --> 06:10.360
Otherwise, you'll get an allergic reaction

06:10.440 --> 06:11.600
to the cream in it.

06:12.760 --> 06:13.600
I…

06:14.960 --> 06:17.520
Is he saying that he wants
to celebrate my birthday with me?

06:26.760 --> 06:28.880
Our birthdays are pretty close.

06:33.200 --> 06:35.000
How do you plan
to celebrate your birthday?

06:36.960 --> 06:38.040
I'm not celebrating it.

06:38.920 --> 06:39.760
Why?

06:41.000 --> 06:43.560
It's pointless to celebrate it alone.

06:56.720 --> 06:58.960
CHAPTER 15, CONFESSION

06:59.040 --> 07:00.560
ATTRACTION

07:04.400 --> 07:06.000
What's the matter with Sangsang?

07:06.080 --> 07:07.520
She hasn't texted us yet.

07:07.600 --> 07:09.280
I wonder how her date went.

07:09.760 --> 07:11.360
You're so nosy.

07:14.200 --> 07:15.040
Do you have a cold?

07:15.920 --> 07:16.760
No.

07:17.320 --> 07:19.320
I have minor symptoms. This will fix it.

07:20.640 --> 07:21.760
You don't understand.

07:22.320 --> 07:23.640
It's more interesting

07:23.720 --> 07:25.840
to observe other people's relationships.

07:25.920 --> 07:27.080
Besides,

07:27.160 --> 07:30.120
not all crushes reciprocate your feelings.

07:30.200 --> 07:32.560
Moreover, this is their first date.

07:32.640 --> 07:33.680
Thinking back on it,

07:33.760 --> 07:36.320
Sangsang was afraid to even tell him
that she likes him.

07:36.400 --> 07:37.400
She was so passive.

07:38.560 --> 07:39.800
If I were in her shoes,

07:39.880 --> 07:41.840
I would've rushed forward

07:41.920 --> 07:42.760
and confessed to him.

07:42.840 --> 07:43.960
Who cares?

07:44.040 --> 07:45.200
I would chase him first.

07:45.280 --> 07:46.360
Sure.

07:46.440 --> 07:47.800
That only works on your boyfriend.

07:47.880 --> 07:48.840
How would you know?

07:49.400 --> 07:50.680
Let me ask you this then.

07:50.760 --> 07:52.400
What would you do if you had a crush

07:52.480 --> 07:53.320
on someone?

07:54.080 --> 07:55.200
You asked the wrong question.

07:55.280 --> 07:56.320
I don't have crushes.

07:56.400 --> 07:57.840
I either like him or I don't.

07:57.920 --> 07:59.880
Okay, let me rephrase my question.

07:59.960 --> 08:02.320
If you like someone,

08:02.400 --> 08:03.760
would you chase him or not?

08:03.840 --> 08:04.960
I wouldn't.

08:06.000 --> 08:07.440
Why should I chase him

08:07.520 --> 08:08.680
if he never gave me any hints?

08:08.760 --> 08:10.560
Why wouldn't you chase him?

08:10.640 --> 08:12.440
What if he has the same mindset as you

08:12.520 --> 08:13.840
and neither of you make a move?

08:13.920 --> 08:15.720
Neither of you will know anything.

08:15.800 --> 08:17.440
I'm sure you'll regret it if he gets taken

08:17.520 --> 08:18.440
by another girl.

08:18.520 --> 08:21.040
If someone else wins him over,

08:21.120 --> 08:22.200
that means he wasn't mine.

08:22.280 --> 08:23.320
There's nothing to regret.

08:23.400 --> 08:24.840
There are plenty of fish in the sea.

08:24.920 --> 08:25.960
Let me ask you this.

08:26.040 --> 08:27.920
If you like a guy,

08:28.400 --> 08:30.240
would you chase him or not?

08:30.880 --> 08:32.240
Would you chase him or not?

08:33.799 --> 08:35.200
I…

08:35.280 --> 08:36.679
I don't know either.

08:37.559 --> 08:38.600
What do you mean?

08:38.679 --> 08:40.159
You asked the wrong person.

08:47.120 --> 08:48.920
Who will join me in the library tomorrow?

08:49.000 --> 08:50.520
- Me.
- Me.

08:51.160 --> 08:53.040
I'll ask Sangsang to join us tomorrow.

08:53.120 --> 08:53.960
Okay.

08:58.120 --> 08:59.920
We already finished supper for some time.

09:00.600 --> 09:01.880
Why isn't Sangsang back yet?

09:03.520 --> 09:04.800
Don't tell me she and her crush

09:04.880 --> 09:06.120
went somewhere else.

09:06.200 --> 09:07.520
I don't think so.

09:07.600 --> 09:10.200
Moreover, this is their first date.

09:11.440 --> 09:12.320
It's so late.

09:12.400 --> 09:13.640
Why hasn't she returned yet?

09:14.120 --> 09:15.080
Call her.

09:20.640 --> 09:22.120
Sangsang, where are you?

09:22.200 --> 09:23.200
- It's late--
- Hello?

09:25.280 --> 09:26.200
Wait.

09:26.280 --> 09:27.800
What is up with the getup?

09:27.880 --> 09:28.840
What's wrong?

09:28.920 --> 09:30.080
I'm fine.

09:30.160 --> 09:32.120
I had an allergic reaction to milk tea.

09:32.200 --> 09:33.560
- Wait!
- What?

09:33.640 --> 09:35.120
Why did you have milk tea?

09:35.800 --> 09:37.440
I only took a sip.

09:38.160 --> 09:40.200
Look at the rashes! How are you okay?

09:40.280 --> 09:41.480
You went on a date

09:41.560 --> 09:42.960
looking like that.

09:43.040 --> 09:43.920
How did it go?

09:44.800 --> 09:45.960
How did it go?

09:50.520 --> 09:51.400
Was it okay?

09:53.120 --> 09:54.000
Wait!

09:55.240 --> 09:56.440
Tell me how okay it was.

09:57.640 --> 09:59.080
I just

09:59.720 --> 10:01.120
feel that…

10:01.600 --> 10:02.640
Tell us.

10:03.680 --> 10:05.120
I feel that he likes me too.

10:05.720 --> 10:06.760
Really?

10:06.840 --> 10:08.520
Does he know that you like him too?

10:08.600 --> 10:09.520
No.

10:09.600 --> 10:11.120
I've never expressed it.

10:13.240 --> 10:15.000
I'm sure he knows that you like him

10:15.080 --> 10:16.680
if he saw you smile like this.

10:18.320 --> 10:19.440
But Sangsang,

10:19.520 --> 10:20.840
you mustn't let him know

10:20.920 --> 10:22.480
that you still like him going forward.

10:23.040 --> 10:24.160
In a relationship,

10:24.240 --> 10:26.360
you want to be the one being pursued.

10:29.320 --> 10:30.400
But what if

10:31.360 --> 10:32.440
he doesn't pursue me?

10:32.520 --> 10:34.320
I don't think that will happen.

10:34.400 --> 10:36.240
Trust me this time.

10:36.320 --> 10:37.520
Trust her this time.

10:37.600 --> 10:38.560
It will work.

10:38.640 --> 10:39.520
It will be fine.

10:39.600 --> 10:40.600
Just trust me this time.

10:40.680 --> 10:41.520
I'm definitely right.

10:42.280 --> 10:43.160
Okay then.

10:44.160 --> 10:45.360
I'll wait for him to pursue me.

10:45.440 --> 10:46.640
That's right.

10:46.720 --> 10:48.080
If he doesn't pursue me,

10:49.000 --> 10:50.360
I'll pursue him.

10:52.240 --> 10:53.360
That was a waste of my time.

10:55.160 --> 10:56.240
You're hopeless.

10:56.840 --> 10:58.720
Your face! Hurry and take your medicine.

10:58.800 --> 10:59.920
It's so red.

11:01.400 --> 11:02.400
Sangsang, you can do it.

11:05.120 --> 11:07.760
MARCH 16TH, FRIDAY

11:07.840 --> 11:10.440
HE CALLED ME HIS FRIEND

11:10.520 --> 11:12.680
INSTEAD OF HIS LITTLE SISTER

11:15.200 --> 11:16.440
Are you waiting at the entrance?

11:16.960 --> 11:18.120
Okay.

11:18.200 --> 11:19.040
I'll head there.

11:38.800 --> 11:39.880
Sang Zhi.

11:42.760 --> 11:44.280
- Jiang Ming.
- Happy birthday.

11:45.080 --> 11:46.120
Your birthday present.

11:49.640 --> 11:51.760
Thank you, but I won't take it.

11:52.320 --> 11:53.320
I already bought it.

11:53.400 --> 11:54.880
I'll be in an awkward spot

11:54.960 --> 11:55.920
if you don't accept it.

11:56.480 --> 11:57.400
Just take it.

12:00.160 --> 12:01.720
Okay then. Thank you.

12:01.800 --> 12:03.680
Are you free later? Let's celebrate.

12:10.800 --> 12:11.680
Hello.

12:15.840 --> 12:17.320
I'll go then.

12:17.400 --> 12:18.360
Have a happy birthday.

12:19.040 --> 12:20.120
Thank you.

12:20.200 --> 12:21.040
Bye.

12:48.360 --> 12:49.480
I'll hold it for you.

13:02.040 --> 13:04.840
Is he the manly man you meant?

13:05.520 --> 13:06.760
I told you already.

13:06.840 --> 13:07.880
It's not him.

13:10.160 --> 13:11.080
Is that so?

13:18.920 --> 13:20.120
Take a look.

13:24.080 --> 13:25.600
Did you take a clear look?

13:25.680 --> 13:26.640
What are you doing?

13:28.520 --> 13:29.480
Look at me.

13:30.440 --> 13:31.880
Do I look like

13:32.720 --> 13:33.800
the man you described?

13:35.920 --> 13:37.600
What is he talking about?

13:39.280 --> 13:40.360
What does he mean?

13:41.400 --> 13:43.240
Does he know already?

13:46.520 --> 13:48.920
No, I cannot admit it.

13:50.600 --> 13:51.960
If I do,

13:52.040 --> 13:53.400
it would be as good as telling him

13:53.880 --> 13:55.440
that I've had a crush on him all along.

13:58.320 --> 13:59.200
No.

14:02.240 --> 14:03.440
Is that so?

14:10.040 --> 14:12.080
Jiaxu, you should

14:12.160 --> 14:14.040
stop mentioning him to me again.

14:14.120 --> 14:16.840
You told me that he is a jerk, right?

14:16.920 --> 14:18.360
That's why I stopped contacting him.

14:19.400 --> 14:20.280
Now,

14:21.360 --> 14:23.040
there isn't anyone I like.

14:30.520 --> 14:33.440
You said that he is a ladies' man.

14:34.040 --> 14:35.080
When did I…

14:39.920 --> 14:42.160
Did I tell him that that day?

14:47.280 --> 14:48.280
Yes, a little.

14:49.120 --> 14:51.240
Do you even know what that term means?

14:52.560 --> 14:53.960
Jiaxu, don't you know what it means?

14:56.040 --> 14:57.400
I told you.

14:57.480 --> 14:58.760
You should go online more often.

14:58.840 --> 15:00.360
Our generation gap is becoming obvious.

15:01.080 --> 15:02.280
Tell me then.

15:02.360 --> 15:03.640
What does the term mean?

15:05.280 --> 15:06.600
It means

15:08.760 --> 15:13.680
a guy with many female friends.

15:15.160 --> 15:17.360
He's nice to all women.

15:18.320 --> 15:20.520
And he doesn't have a girlfriend.

15:22.560 --> 15:24.360
If a guy fulfills
one of these three criteria,

15:24.440 --> 15:26.280
does that make him a ladies' man?

15:26.360 --> 15:28.280
Of course not. It must be all three.

15:35.200 --> 15:36.920
You're pretty good at framing people.

15:37.560 --> 15:38.920
What did you say?

15:41.720 --> 15:42.920
Did I say anything?

15:44.560 --> 15:45.880
You did just now.

15:58.920 --> 16:00.200
002 BOUND FOR HONGXI BUS TERMINAL

16:01.040 --> 16:02.400
This is strange.

16:02.480 --> 16:03.640
Why was the movie in theaters

16:03.720 --> 16:04.840
for such a short time only?

16:06.080 --> 16:07.480
It's all because you were too busy.

16:10.720 --> 16:12.120
Are you blaming me then?

16:14.600 --> 16:15.720
No.

16:16.280 --> 16:17.480
This is pretty good too.

16:17.560 --> 16:19.080
The theater downtown

16:19.160 --> 16:20.920
has bigger screens and better acoustics.

16:21.000 --> 16:22.520
And it's your birthday.

16:23.360 --> 16:24.760
That makes it more meaningful.

16:49.080 --> 16:49.920
Hold onto me

16:50.000 --> 16:50.960
so you don't fall.

17:09.079 --> 17:09.920
Hold tight.

18:05.000 --> 18:06.800
You want to get a drink again, don't you?

18:06.880 --> 18:08.320
You're not having any anyway.

18:09.400 --> 18:11.640
Aren't you afraid of blushing again?

18:13.520 --> 18:15.520
It was an allergic reaction,

18:15.600 --> 18:16.760
not blushing.

18:18.320 --> 18:20.000
- Hi. What would you like to order?
- Hello.

18:20.760 --> 18:23.720
A girl with square glasses works here.

18:23.800 --> 18:25.000
Is she here today?

18:25.080 --> 18:28.400
- She's on the night shift today.
- I want lemon tea with boba.

18:28.480 --> 18:29.320
Okay. Hot or iced?

18:29.400 --> 18:30.240
Iced.

18:30.320 --> 18:31.480
Hot.

18:32.200 --> 18:33.320
Make it hot.

18:33.400 --> 18:35.000
It's too cold for iced beverages.

18:35.080 --> 18:36.560
I want it iced.

18:36.640 --> 18:37.480
Okay.

18:37.560 --> 18:38.800
It's stuffy in the theater.

18:39.920 --> 18:41.720
Iced lemon tea with boba.

18:41.800 --> 18:44.040
Fine, you can have it.

18:44.520 --> 18:46.080
- Here.
- I'll scan your phone.

18:47.120 --> 18:48.640
It will be cold in the theater later.

18:48.720 --> 18:50.200
The air-conditioning is strong.

18:50.280 --> 18:51.440
Don't drink too much.

18:52.520 --> 18:53.840
Mind your own business.

18:54.400 --> 18:55.840
Do you find me annoying?

18:55.920 --> 18:57.120
No.

18:57.200 --> 18:58.560
Wasn't that what you meant?

18:59.360 --> 19:00.280
No.

19:02.120 --> 19:03.120
You should get used to it.

19:09.400 --> 19:10.400
Thank you.

19:14.560 --> 19:15.440
Have a good day.

19:23.360 --> 19:24.280
Over there.

19:47.320 --> 19:48.560
I'll hold it for you.

19:53.280 --> 19:54.520
Do you want to drink it?

20:01.120 --> 20:02.520
I can hold it myself.

20:03.080 --> 20:04.320
You…

20:05.120 --> 20:07.080
You can drink your drink.

20:07.160 --> 20:08.600
Why did you touch my hand on purpose?

20:20.520 --> 20:22.760
I can actually hold it myself.

20:22.840 --> 20:24.120
Aren't you afraid of cold hands?

20:25.080 --> 20:26.720
Won't you get cold hands too?

20:29.680 --> 20:30.520
You're right.

20:33.160 --> 20:34.640
You can warm it up for me.

20:44.400 --> 20:45.440
I don't think

20:46.880 --> 20:47.720
it is

20:49.280 --> 20:50.880
appropriate

20:51.720 --> 20:52.880
for us to do that.

20:59.520 --> 21:01.440
You're right.

21:05.040 --> 21:06.640
After all, we haven't put a label on it.

21:08.920 --> 21:09.840
Label?

21:31.800 --> 21:32.680
Here you go.

21:32.760 --> 21:33.640
Wipe your hands.

21:51.520 --> 21:52.360
Hold it.

22:28.360 --> 22:29.280
- Zhizhi.
- Jiaxu.

22:32.120 --> 22:32.960
You first.

22:34.760 --> 22:35.600
It's nothing.

22:35.680 --> 22:37.600
I just want to ask you
where we're going later.

22:38.360 --> 22:39.560
Let's go

22:39.640 --> 22:40.680
to my place later.

22:45.760 --> 22:47.760
My gift for you is at my place.

22:47.840 --> 22:49.040
And then,

22:49.120 --> 22:50.760
we can eat some cake together.

22:54.600 --> 22:55.480
Jiaxu.

22:56.880 --> 22:58.320
Do you want me to go to your place?

23:02.800 --> 23:04.720
Didn't you tell me before

23:04.800 --> 23:07.080
not to visit you at your place or office?

23:08.080 --> 23:09.760
When did I say something like that?

23:12.280 --> 23:13.440
That time

23:13.520 --> 23:15.280
when I brought you the peephole camera.

23:15.840 --> 23:17.800
You pulled me off to one side and told me

23:17.880 --> 23:20.640
not to visit you
at your place or office again.

23:24.240 --> 23:25.200
That time?

23:27.640 --> 23:28.920
It's like this.

23:29.000 --> 23:29.880
Jiang Ying

23:29.960 --> 23:31.560
suddenly came to find me at my office.

23:32.120 --> 23:33.960
I was afraid she might hurt you

23:34.040 --> 23:35.880
if she saw you.

23:35.960 --> 23:37.040
That's why…

23:39.720 --> 23:40.640
But it's true.

23:40.720 --> 23:42.120
I was too hasty that day.

23:42.200 --> 23:43.760
I may not have made myself clear.

23:50.360 --> 23:53.440
So you've been upset lately

23:54.080 --> 23:55.400
because of this?

24:04.800 --> 24:06.320
You're making it sound

24:07.200 --> 24:09.320
as if I'm a petty person.

24:11.960 --> 24:12.880
No.

24:12.960 --> 24:15.120
This was indeed my fault.

24:15.680 --> 24:17.680
I should've explained it to you clearly.

24:17.760 --> 24:19.880
Let me apologize to you.

24:30.080 --> 24:31.120
I guess

24:31.680 --> 24:33.920
I was being a bit petty too.

24:35.520 --> 24:36.480
I apologize to you too.

24:37.120 --> 24:38.040
I'm sorry.

24:40.040 --> 24:41.920
So now, the misunderstanding is resolved.

24:42.760 --> 24:43.640
Let's go eat cake.

24:45.600 --> 24:46.640
Let's go.

25:07.760 --> 25:08.800
I prepared these for you.

25:10.640 --> 25:11.680
For me?

25:15.120 --> 25:16.040
They are pretty nice.

25:19.600 --> 25:20.680
Don't change into them yet.

25:21.760 --> 25:23.600
You haven't been to the rooftop, right?

25:23.680 --> 25:24.640
Go and check it out.

26:07.360 --> 26:09.040
Why are there two cakes?

26:10.080 --> 26:11.480
I made one of them.

26:11.560 --> 26:12.720
It doesn't contain any dairy,

26:12.800 --> 26:13.760
so you can eat it.

26:16.240 --> 26:17.720
It's this one, right?

26:19.480 --> 26:20.960
Can you tell?

26:21.040 --> 26:21.920
It's pretty obvious.

26:22.800 --> 26:25.120
So why did you also buy this one?

26:25.920 --> 26:27.680
I was afraid mine would turn out ugly,

26:27.760 --> 26:29.760
so I bought another one
to stick your candles in.

26:30.960 --> 26:32.560
It's not ugly. It looks great.

26:32.640 --> 26:33.520
Is that so?

26:34.520 --> 26:36.560
Then pick one to stick your candles in.

26:38.040 --> 26:40.200
Then I'll go

26:41.200 --> 26:42.120
with this one.

26:46.440 --> 26:47.400
Okay.

26:50.720 --> 26:52.120
How many candles do you want?

26:52.200 --> 26:53.480
One is enough.

26:53.560 --> 26:54.440
- This one--
- No way.

26:56.120 --> 26:57.160
You need 19 candles.

26:57.720 --> 26:59.360
You need to know your own age.

27:03.800 --> 27:04.680
Jiaxu.

27:05.640 --> 27:07.400
If we have to know our own age

27:07.920 --> 27:09.240
when we celebrate our birthdays,

27:09.320 --> 27:10.560
I don't think

27:10.640 --> 27:12.640
there will be enough candles for you.

27:18.160 --> 27:19.840
You just have to mock my age every day.

27:47.840 --> 27:49.920
Happy birthday to you

27:50.520 --> 27:52.840
Happy birthday to you

27:52.920 --> 27:55.920
Happy birthday to you

27:56.000 --> 27:57.840
Happy birthday to you

27:59.880 --> 28:01.920
This is the first birthday

28:02.000 --> 28:03.720
that I'm spending with Jiaxu.

28:04.360 --> 28:05.360
I hope

28:05.440 --> 28:07.240
there will be many more to come.

28:10.000 --> 28:11.000
Make a wish.

28:14.520 --> 28:15.720
Can I say it out loud?

28:16.880 --> 28:17.960
Do you want to?

28:36.120 --> 28:37.200
Happy birthday!

28:40.760 --> 28:41.600
Cut the cake.

28:43.040 --> 28:44.680
Make the first cut.

28:46.400 --> 28:47.280
Okay.

29:04.400 --> 29:05.400
Here.

29:06.560 --> 29:08.640
Sang Zhi, you're officially 19 years old.

29:09.400 --> 29:11.160
Try it. See if it tastes good.

29:22.800 --> 29:23.720
Does it taste good?

29:24.680 --> 29:25.560
It's delicious.

29:25.640 --> 29:27.480
It's just the same as that one. Delicious.

29:28.520 --> 29:29.400
Great.

29:31.640 --> 29:32.600
Your birthday present.

29:36.240 --> 29:37.600
You already made a cake for me.

29:37.680 --> 29:38.600
Do I get a gift too?

29:38.680 --> 29:41.440
The cake will only last for a while.

29:41.520 --> 29:43.360
A present should last longer.

29:44.440 --> 29:45.600
Thank you, Jiaxu.

29:49.680 --> 29:52.120
You can open it when you get back.

29:54.680 --> 29:55.640
Okay.

29:58.080 --> 29:59.280
I'll try a slice too.

30:24.680 --> 30:26.200
Did someone give that to you?

30:26.800 --> 30:27.880
Aren't you going to open it?

30:30.040 --> 30:31.160
I'll do it when I get back.

30:34.120 --> 30:35.520
Is that guy trying to pursue you?

30:38.320 --> 30:40.360
It looks like you're pretty popular.

30:48.000 --> 30:49.320
So can you tell me

30:50.120 --> 30:51.440
what it takes

30:52.280 --> 30:53.360
for a guy to pursue you?

30:58.920 --> 31:00.640
What? That's nonsense.

31:02.800 --> 31:04.000
Then tell me.

31:04.760 --> 31:06.480
What do you look for

31:07.240 --> 31:08.240
in a guy?

31:16.400 --> 31:17.400
He must be handsome,

31:20.400 --> 31:21.320
have a good temper,

31:23.600 --> 31:24.520
and…

31:29.120 --> 31:30.520
He must be a head taller than me.

31:32.480 --> 31:33.760
Anything else?

31:34.880 --> 31:36.200
And…

31:37.560 --> 31:39.200
He must have morals. That's all.

31:39.760 --> 31:40.640
Is that all?

31:49.320 --> 31:50.280
I think

31:51.360 --> 31:53.880
I check all these boxes.

31:56.920 --> 31:58.240
So I want to ask you something.

32:05.840 --> 32:07.080
Can I pursue you?

32:29.640 --> 32:30.520
I…

32:32.680 --> 32:33.600
I…

32:34.200 --> 32:35.160
Jiaxu.

32:36.520 --> 32:38.800
Does what you said

32:40.040 --> 32:43.640
mean the same as what I think it means?

32:45.040 --> 32:47.120
Is there another meaning to it?

32:51.520 --> 32:53.040
But didn't you say

32:54.760 --> 32:55.920
that I'm a kiddo?

32:57.080 --> 32:58.400
You think I'm too young.

32:59.800 --> 33:01.520
That is just a nickname.

33:01.600 --> 33:02.840
If you like it,

33:02.920 --> 33:04.880
I can call you that even when you're 80.

33:06.400 --> 33:07.240
Besides,

33:07.920 --> 33:09.760
you call me your brother all the time.

33:09.840 --> 33:11.560
Do you really consider me your brother?

33:14.200 --> 33:15.640
I do consider you my brother.

33:18.720 --> 33:19.600
But

33:20.480 --> 33:22.520
I don't want to be just your brother.

33:23.600 --> 33:25.200
I want to be your boyfriend.

33:48.160 --> 33:49.640
Say something.

33:50.200 --> 33:51.280
If you don't say something,

33:52.640 --> 33:54.120
I don't think I can breathe.

33:56.080 --> 33:57.200
You can't breathe?

33:58.600 --> 33:59.720
More like

34:00.520 --> 34:01.920
I can't breathe.

34:06.520 --> 34:07.480
Jiaxu.

34:08.719 --> 34:10.040
No one asks for permission

34:10.120 --> 34:12.320
before pursuing someone.

34:13.679 --> 34:15.920
I have to make myself clear.

34:16.679 --> 34:18.719
Otherwise, what will I do
if you think I'm good to you

34:18.800 --> 34:20.440
because I'm your elder?

34:21.639 --> 34:23.159
That's your business.

34:23.239 --> 34:24.920
It has nothing to do with me.

34:28.239 --> 34:29.600
Why don't you just tell me?

34:30.480 --> 34:31.480
Tell me

34:31.960 --> 34:34.280
if you feel that way about me.

34:41.719 --> 34:42.560
No.

34:45.280 --> 34:46.159
However,

34:47.600 --> 34:49.199
what I mean is

34:50.080 --> 34:51.360
that I won't know

34:52.120 --> 34:53.920
if I feel that way about you

34:54.520 --> 34:55.880
until you pursue me.

35:02.320 --> 35:03.160
Sure.

35:04.720 --> 35:07.480
Then can you give me a hint first?

35:08.040 --> 35:09.920
How long do I need to pursue you?

35:11.000 --> 35:12.360
How can I give you a hint?

35:12.920 --> 35:15.040
You make it sound
as if I'll say yes for sure.

35:16.320 --> 35:17.200
How could you say no?

35:17.280 --> 35:18.520
You won't win me over.

35:18.600 --> 35:19.440
I'm tough to please.

35:20.760 --> 35:21.920
Fine.

35:22.000 --> 35:23.360
Then I'll drag it out.

35:23.920 --> 35:25.480
I'll pursue you for a decade or so.

35:27.520 --> 35:30.800
But if you go and meet other guys,

35:30.880 --> 35:33.160
I'll complain to your parents.

35:35.600 --> 35:37.040
Why would you complain to them?

35:37.640 --> 35:39.160
Did you forget the time

35:39.240 --> 35:41.160
when I met your teacher as your guardian?

35:43.120 --> 35:44.440
That was ages ago.

35:44.520 --> 35:45.560
Why are you bringing it up?

35:46.640 --> 35:48.000
I'm a nostalgic person.

35:50.000 --> 35:50.840
By the way,

35:51.360 --> 35:52.840
I forgot to tell you this.

35:52.920 --> 35:55.280
You look pretty today.

36:03.280 --> 36:04.200
I know.

36:06.160 --> 36:07.840
You dressed up to see me.

36:08.440 --> 36:10.000
Then you say you have no feelings for me.

36:11.680 --> 36:13.680
Can't I make myself pretty on my birthday?

36:14.360 --> 36:16.920
Did you think I dressed up for you?

36:17.000 --> 36:18.120
Fine.

36:18.200 --> 36:19.920
I know you don't have feelings for me.

36:20.000 --> 36:21.280
Can't I imagine things

36:21.360 --> 36:22.360
and make myself happy?

36:22.440 --> 36:24.120
Then keep it to yourself.

36:24.680 --> 36:26.080
I want to say it out loud,

36:26.160 --> 36:27.280
so that you know.

36:41.200 --> 36:42.440
By the way, Jiaxu.

36:44.640 --> 36:45.680
You…

36:46.800 --> 36:48.240
You didn't

36:48.320 --> 36:49.680
confess to me today, right?

36:50.160 --> 36:51.200
You only asked me

36:51.280 --> 36:52.400
whether you could pursue me.

36:52.880 --> 36:54.640
I technically didn't reject you,

36:54.720 --> 36:55.680
right?

36:56.240 --> 36:57.640
So then,

36:57.720 --> 36:58.960
can I take the cake with me?

37:03.360 --> 37:04.240
Then

37:05.040 --> 37:06.680
are you saying

37:07.400 --> 37:09.320
that I confess to you right now,

37:09.400 --> 37:11.160
- you will say yes?
- No.

37:11.240 --> 37:12.560
Then you can't take it.

37:13.880 --> 37:15.320
You can keep this one.

37:15.400 --> 37:17.640
I'll take this one, all right?

37:17.720 --> 37:18.600
No.

37:18.680 --> 37:20.720
Why are you so petty?

37:20.800 --> 37:21.920
I'm just saying

37:22.000 --> 37:23.520
that you can pursue me a little more.

37:23.600 --> 37:24.720
It's not like I didn't agree…

37:29.400 --> 37:30.440
I…

37:30.520 --> 37:31.840
You have to pursue me first

37:32.600 --> 37:33.720
before I can know

37:33.800 --> 37:35.760
if I feel that way about you.

37:36.560 --> 37:37.480
Do you understand?

37:38.760 --> 37:39.880
Fine.

37:40.440 --> 37:41.840
That's okay.

37:41.920 --> 37:43.320
If you don't feel that way about me,

37:43.400 --> 37:44.920
I'll keep pursuing you.

37:47.520 --> 37:48.640
Eat the cake.

37:52.120 --> 37:53.880
Sit down and enjoy it.

38:01.400 --> 38:03.160
You can take the cake with you.

38:07.680 --> 38:08.760
Both of them?

38:11.120 --> 38:12.000
If you like it,

38:12.480 --> 38:14.320
I can make it for you every day.

38:20.480 --> 38:21.360
Sure.

38:41.400 --> 38:42.480
I'm back!

38:48.160 --> 38:49.320
Are you guys asleep?

38:51.000 --> 38:51.840
It's pretty early.

39:00.120 --> 39:01.760
I'm back.

39:01.840 --> 39:05.400
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

39:05.480 --> 39:08.520
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

39:08.600 --> 39:11.960
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

39:12.040 --> 39:14.400
- Happy birthday to you
- Happy birthday to you

39:15.960 --> 39:17.120
- Make a wish!
- Make a wish!

39:17.200 --> 39:18.040
Hurry!

39:20.360 --> 39:21.280
Can I say it out loud?

39:21.360 --> 39:22.640
- No.
- No.

39:22.720 --> 39:23.880
Blow out the candle.

39:26.160 --> 39:27.520
Happy birthday!

39:27.600 --> 39:29.760
- You're another year older now.
- Put it down.

39:30.960 --> 39:32.480
Why do you have two cakes?

39:33.400 --> 39:35.840
This one looks terrible!

39:35.920 --> 39:36.760
No, it's not.

39:36.840 --> 39:38.240
I think it looks adorable.

39:40.040 --> 39:41.560
Don't tell me

39:41.640 --> 39:43.280
that your crush made it for you.

39:44.800 --> 39:45.920
Is it that obvious?

39:46.000 --> 39:47.440
Really?

39:48.400 --> 39:50.360
Did your date go well today?

39:51.560 --> 39:52.600
Tell us about it.

39:53.720 --> 39:55.000
I did have a good time.

39:56.040 --> 39:57.080
If so,

39:57.160 --> 39:59.000
was there any substantial progress?

40:01.680 --> 40:02.600
Yes.

40:03.920 --> 40:05.680
I knew it!

40:05.760 --> 40:07.440
- Tell us!
- Spill it!

40:07.520 --> 40:08.360
- Hurry.
- Tell us.

40:08.440 --> 40:09.320
I…

40:09.920 --> 40:10.760
What is it?

40:11.400 --> 40:12.600
I think you guys understand.

40:16.120 --> 40:17.440
I can't take it anymore. Come on.

40:17.520 --> 40:18.520
He's so good at this.

40:41.440 --> 40:42.760
Put your back into it.

40:42.840 --> 40:44.080
Knead it repeatedly.

40:44.160 --> 40:46.360
Yes, knead it into the shape of a circle,

40:46.440 --> 40:47.560
then roll it out.

40:52.960 --> 40:53.840
No, not like that.

40:53.920 --> 40:55.520
Here, let me show you.

40:55.600 --> 40:57.040
Roll it out forward.

40:57.800 --> 40:59.000
When you're almost to the end,

40:59.080 --> 41:00.080
you have to roll it back.

41:00.160 --> 41:01.720
You can't just roll in one direction.

41:01.800 --> 41:03.120
- Got it?
- Okay, let me try.

41:08.000 --> 41:09.440
You refused to learn this

41:09.520 --> 41:10.680
when you worked at my shop

41:11.280 --> 41:12.400
when you were in 12th grade.

41:12.480 --> 41:14.320
Now you're suddenly back to learn it.

41:14.880 --> 41:16.120
Are you seeing someone?

41:19.880 --> 41:20.840
Am I right?

41:23.400 --> 41:24.440
You brat.

41:26.360 --> 41:27.240
Listen.

41:28.040 --> 41:29.440
A cake that you put your heart into

41:29.520 --> 41:30.800
will taste different.

41:32.360 --> 41:33.320
Remember that.

41:34.000 --> 41:35.480
Okay, flatten it out.

41:36.160 --> 41:37.640
That's right. Forward and backward.

41:37.720 --> 41:39.520
Be careful. That's it.

41:46.560 --> 41:47.920
Why is it cracked?

41:48.480 --> 41:49.600
Did I bake it for too long?

41:50.720 --> 41:51.600
Listen.

41:52.480 --> 41:53.440
Don't be discouraged.

41:53.520 --> 41:55.000
It's a tough one to make.

41:55.080 --> 41:56.240
You should've listened to me

41:56.320 --> 41:58.000
and made something simpler.

41:58.080 --> 41:59.960
It's fine. I'll try again.
